features.text:
# Welcome to Vox Walk

The most awesome voxel wearables department store in the metaverse

We currently have residents from Australia, Asia, Europe, North America and South America.  WOW :)

Sign the guess book, join the discord and follow on Twitter

collectible.name: CV Wearables: Treasure Chest - Mimic
collectible.description: This is a mimic treasure chest for playing treasure hunt. You can use it too to decore an ambient. If you are a meta-architect, you can find many uses for this chest. Created by Gustavo Manute and branded by The Philosopher.
collectible.author: 0xe9956cf72cc8e49d903478142dc8dadb4ee328ff

collectible.name: CV Wearable 1/1: VOX WALK JUDGES TABLE
collectible.description: Created by The Alchemist and branded by The Philosopher, this Vox Walk Table was made specially for the judges from the car contest, at 10th September, 2021, sponsored by Tpae and organized by Vox Walk and The Philosopher. This is a historical and unique table.
